    "description": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The atmosphere of the game</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >you can craft bombs and health packs using resources found in the environment.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031980/extras/868d7749f6f3865354380aefc1865696.avif?t=1751935205\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031980/extras_big/868d7749f6f3865354380aefc1865696.avif?t=1751935205 width=800 height=550 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You earn money by killing enemies and through other means, allowing you to buy anything you need from the shop.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031980/extras/96b2662e145630ee8e011c6249bdb5d2.poster.avif?t=1751935205\" width=320 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031980/extras/96b2662e145630ee8e011c6249bdb5d2.webm?t=1751935205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031980/extras/96b2662e145630ee8e011c6249bdb5d2.mp4?t=1751935205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enter the world of <strong>AWAKE</strong> and experience an environment full of mystery and horror. Fight with mutants and zombies and find a way to escape with guns, bullets and blood. Those who have left the <strong>AWAKE</strong> world alive are less than the number of fingers, that is where it all ends. A moment without a weapon in the <strong>AWAKE</strong> means death. Passing through narrow and dark tunnels and the song of zombies, which smells of death, eats away at the human soul.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have to pass through poisonous gases. Fight with intelligent space robots that have come to earth and save humanity. You have to cross the dragon's territory to save </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                          </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ENEMYES</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >zombie  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shooter zombies </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Flying and fire-throwing dragons </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Various monsters that crawl on two legs or four arms </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rats and big spiders </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alien robots with laser weapons </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Flying robots with cannons and laser weapons </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meat trees with toxic gases </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game mechanics</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, you see blood splattering around with every shot. You use different weapons to kill enemies. You can destroy enemies in groups by throwing grenades and shooting barrels and explosive gas capsules. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Break wooden crates and loot chests and backpacks to collect ammo and health packs </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031980/extras/0b2c3a335fe9e1651925fb2169106ba8.poster.avif?t=1751935205\" width=320 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031980/extras/0b2c3a335fe9e1651925fb2169106ba8.webm?t=1751935205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031980/extras/0b2c3a335fe9e1651925fb2169106ba8.mp4?t=1751935205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Summary of the story of the game</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world has been destroyed by war and governments have fallen. Most of the regions of the earth have been contaminated with deadly gases, nuclear radiation and unknown diseases. People call these regions the awakening region. That is, the place where you must always be awake because if you sleep, you will not wake up again. You enter the game in the role of Yusuf, who is a former employee of the rescue forces. During the chaos a year ago, he lost his wife and child in one of the safe areas, and now a request for help from the awakening area brings him there, because he thinks that this help message was sent by his wife </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   </p>",
